      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction: picture with Sept 15 Classical Music and Dance Guide was published in error; it showed 1996 production of Le Nozze di Figaro, not current New York City Opera production</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture in Weekend on Friday with the Classical Music and Dance Guide was published in error. It showed Michaela Gurevich in a 1996 production of ''Le Nozze di Figaro,'' not Sari Gruber, who sings Susanna in the New York City Opera's current production.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
